# Table Borders üñºÔ∏è

By default, tables have no borders. You add them using CSS.

```html
<style>
table, th, td {
  border: 1px solid black;
}
</style>
```

## Collapsing Borders

To make single borders instead of double lines, use `border-collapse`.

```css
table {
  border-collapse: collapse;
}
```
